{"article_id":"FyQKJhtAmNEG25yX","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"After a whirlwind emergency trip to Saudi Arabia and Turkey , Secretary of State Mike Pompeo told President Donald Trump on Thursday","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that the United States needs to give the Saudis \" a few more days \"","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to investigate the fate of journalist Jamal Khashoggi .","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"\" We made clear to them","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"that we take this matter very seriously , \"","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"Pompeo said","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"after meeting with Trump","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"to brief him on his two-day trip ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"during which he discussed Khashoggi ' s disappearance with top government officials .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"\" They assured me","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that they will conduct a complete and thorough investigation . \"","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Pompeo did not say","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"whether he believes","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Khashoggi is dead .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"\" There are lots of stories out there about what has happened , \"","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Pompeo said .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"\" We just are going to allow the process to move forward ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"allow the facts to unfold . \"","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"After Pompeo ' s brief remarks , Trump tweeted","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"that \" the Saudi situation was discussed in great detail \" in his meeting with the secretary of state .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"He wrote","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"that Pompeo is \" waiting for the results of the investigations","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"being done by the Saudis and Turkey . \"","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"It ' s been more than two weeks since Khashoggi , a Saudi dissident","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"who obtained U.S. residency last year over fears for his safety ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"vanished","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"after visiting the kingdom ' s consulate in Istanbul .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Turkish officials claimed","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"there are gruesome audio and video recordings of Khashoggi","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"being beheaded and dismembered","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"within minutes of entering the compound .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"The Saudi government denied killing the journalist .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Pompeo traveled to the Saudi and Turkish capitals","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"to seek answers in the case","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that has put pressure on the Trump administration .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Trump said Wednesday in the Oval Office","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"that the United States asked Ankara for copies of audio or video evidence of Khashoggi ' s killing ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"`` if it exists . ''","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Pompeo did not say anything about the recordings .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"He expressed confidence","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"that the Saudi government would conduct a full and `` transparent '' investigation ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"and he emphasized America 's decades-long alliance with the Saudi government .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"`` We have a long strategic relationship with Saudi Arabia , ''","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Pompeo said .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"`` We need to be mindful of that . ''","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Trump denied","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"that he ' s \" giving cover \" to Saudi Arabia ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"which cooperates with Washington on oil , anti-terrorism operations and arms sales","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"and acts as a bulwark against the United States ' regional enemy Iran .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"\" I want to find out what happened ,","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"where is the fault ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"and we will probably know that by the end of the week , \"","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Trump said Wednesday .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"Who is Jamal Khashoggi ?","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"Royal court confidant and prominent Saudi journalist turned reluctant dissident","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"In the midst of the diplomatic crisis , Saudi Arabia transferred $ 100 million to the State Department","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"- a long-promised contribution","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"to help stabilize parts of Syria","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"that have been liberated from the Islamic State ,","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"also known as ISIS .","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"The donation came","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"as Pompeo landed in Riyadh","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"to meet with Saudi officials .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"A top State Department official","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"involved in securing the funds","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"there was no connection .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"\" We always expected the contribution to be finalized in the fall timeframe , \"","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"said Dan McGurk , the president ' s special envoy for the Global Coalition to Defeat ISIS .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"\" The specific transfer of funds has been long in process","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"and has nothing","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to do with other events or the secretary ' s visit . \"","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"The Saudis made the $ 100 million pledge in August ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"and McGurk was in Riyadh on Oct. 12","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"working to finalize the transfer .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"Trump floated the idea","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"that Khashoggi may have been killed by `` rogue killers . ''","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"The pro-government Turkish newspaper Yeni Safak claimed Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"that the 60-year-old journalist","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"who wrote for The Washington Post","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"was accosted by a team of Saudi agents","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"immediately upon entering the consulate ,","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"who cut off his fingers","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"and decapitated him .","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"Thursday , Sabah , a Turkish newspaper with close government ties , published surveillance video images","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"showing a man","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"who traveled with Saudi Arabia 's crown prince on a visit to the USA in March","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"walking into the Saudi consulate in Istanbul","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"shortly before Khashoggi disappeared .","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"\" If a country engages in activity","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"that is unlawful ,","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"it ' s unacceptable .","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"No one is going to defend activity of that nature , \"","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"Pompeo said in Turkey Wednesday","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"after holding talks with President Recep Tayyip Erdogan .","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"A State Department spokeswoman said","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"Pompeo had not reviewed the recordings","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"Turkish security officials claimed to possess .","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"On his way home to Washington from Turkey on Wednesday , Pompeo acknowledged growing calls for answers :","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"`` Sooner ' s better than later for everyone . ''","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"Turkish investigators searched the Istanbul home of the Saudi consul general and the consulate","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"where Khashoggi was allegedly killed","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"for clues","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"but revealed little about what they discovered .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"The consul left Turkey this week .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"The last column","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"Jamal Khashoggi wrote","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"before disappearing","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"focuses on need for free press","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"More :","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"Trump vows","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"US will not ' walk away from Saudi Arabia ' amid pressure","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"to respond to Jamal Khashoggi ' s alleged murder","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"More :","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"' Do this outside ' :","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"New claims over Saudi Arabia ' s Jamal Khashoggi","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"More :","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"Intimidation , detention , even murder :","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"World is full of many potential Jamal Khashoggis","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman , the de facto ruler of Saudi Arabia , has jailed hundreds of journalists , activists , officials and even members of his own royal family in a bid","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"to quash dissent .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"Thursday , The Washington Post published the last column by Khashoggi ,","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"written shortly before he went missing","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"and sent to the newspaper a day","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"after he disappeared by his translator .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"The column ,","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"titled `` What the Arab world needs most is free expression , ''","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"focuses on the need for a free media in the Middle East .","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"Khashoggi lamented in the piece","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"that many Arabs , in his view , live in a state of misinformation .","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"He wrote about","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"how freedom of the press has been under attack","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"and generally is n't taken seriously by the international community ,","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"and as a result , reporters were being silenced .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"`` These actions no longer carry the consequence of a backlash from the international community , ''","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"Khashoggi wrote .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"`` Instead , these actions may trigger condemnation quickly ,","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"followed by silence .","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"As a result , Arab governments have been given free rein","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"to continue silencing the media . ''","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"More :","depth":2},{"id":143,"text":"US weapons sales a flashpoint","depth":3},{"id":144,"text":"as President Trump presses Saudi Arabia over missing journalist","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":289,"left":286,"right":288,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":197,"right":285,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":167,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":162,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":155,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":147,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":0,"right":146,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":152,"right":153,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":152,"left":149,"right":151,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":148,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":6,"right":150,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":161,"left":157,"right":160,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":1